title: August_Alsina-This_Thing_Called_Life-(2015)
description:
This Thing Called Life is the 2nd album from New Orleans' R&B artist August Alsina. The new record arrives just one year after his acclaimed debut album, Testimony. The LP's lead single "Hip-Hop" was released in April, few monts then the singer dropped the 2nd single "Why I Do It" with Lil Wayne. The 3rd and current single "Song Cry" leaked in October. He teamed up also with Anthony Hamilton, Jadakiss and Chris Brown on the album. Don't forget to support the artist and BUY your copies.
